          "username": "pa834y"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-04-25 19:56:27.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nPlease do. I think the error in junit is due to the server going away before it can do close handshake. We try to keep starting again. Let me try to repoduce in local and I'll try again later in the evening, don't want to keep blocking jenkins job.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
